# ════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
# Patient / device data — NEVER commit these
# ════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

# Date-named backup folders (e.g. 12.1.2025/, 4.10.2024/)
/[0-9]*/

# Trilogy / Tril backup folders (e.g. "trilogy 1.31.2022/", "Tril 077908-17-2025/")
/[Tt]ril*/

# Golden archive directory (wherever it is under the workspace root)
_golden_*/

# EDF data files — safety net
*.edf
*.EDF

# ════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
# Python environment
# ════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
.venv/
__pycache__/
*.pyc
*.pyo

# ════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
# OS / Dropbox artifacts
# ════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
desktop.ini
.dropbox
.dropbox.cache
Thumbs.db

# stray NUL device file (Windows artifact)
null

# SD card staging folders (e.g. "SD card 26-03-18/")
/[Ss][Dd] */

# TOC cache (derived, never committed)
.toc-cache/
